data.description: Charming 2BR/1BA Home with Solar Panels and Fenced Backyard 205 S. 7th St presents a cozy 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence exuding timeless charm. Laminate and hardwood flooring lend character to the space. The property is equipped with fully paid-off solar panels, guaranteeing both eco-friendliness and cost efficiency. Additional perks include two storage buildings and a fenced backyard, offering ample room for outdoor activities. With no HOA fees, you have the freedom to personalize the space. Sold As-Is
